Class ScrollBar

  • java.lang.Object
    • wireframe.AbstractElement
      • wireframe.AbstractWireframeElement
        • wireframe.ScrollBar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Groupable

    public class ScrollBar
extends AbstractWireframeElement
    A ScrollBar element represents a vertical progress bar in a wireframe (like a sidebar). The progress of the ScrollBar can be adjusted.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      ScrollBar(Location location)
      Creates a ScrollBar at specified location with default progress 0%.
